features: 【High cost-effective fuse kit]】-- The fuse kit includes mini type 114 pcs + standard type 54 pcs, both styles of fuses have 11 current specifications (2A /3A / 5A/ 7.5A/ 10A/ 15A/ 20A/ 25A / 30A/ 35A/40A). Equipped with 1 fuse pullers, easy to clip out the fuse.

【Reasonable Quantity Matching】-- According to market research data, we have increased the number of fuses with commonly used current specifications of 10A/ 15A/ 20A/ 25A, and reduced the number of other less-used fuses. The numberof car fuses is reasonable and Extend the use time of the fuse.

【Choose the correct type of fuse】-- German car brands usually use 2 sizes of fuses, other European car brands usually use standard sizes; American and Japanese car brands usually use mini sizes. As there are many types of cars,it is recommended that you use the original car fuse to compare with our fuse size or search for car fuse models on the Internet.

【Installation Instructions】-- The fuse set contains fuse installation instructions to help you replace and install the fuse correctly. The fuse kit is suitable for cars/RVs/truck/motorcycles/boats, etc.

【High quality, easy to identify】-- The auto fuse is made of environmentally friendly plastic and zinc alloy, packaged in a strong and transparent plastic box, which is easy to store and carry. The blade fuse of each current specification is distinguished by different colors, and the current specification number is marked on the top of each fuse, which is easy to identify.
